6
00:00:52,761 --> 00:00:54,388
[thud]
‐ Huh?

7
00:00:54,388 --> 00:00:56,265
‐ What happened to him?
‐ No way!

8
00:00:56,265 --> 00:00:59,101
‐ For now, all I want from you
is one email addy.

9
00:00:59,101 --> 00:01:00,852
Give me that,
and I'll leave you alone.

10
00:01:00,852 --> 00:01:02,854
‐ I need to see you
right now,

11
00:01:02,854 --> 00:01:03,855
and call the others.

12
00:01:03,855 --> 00:01:04,856
I want to see them, too.

13
00:01:04,856 --> 00:01:06,733
‐ And the Dullahan's head, too.

14
00:01:06,733 --> 00:01:08,694
I'll take 'em all.
Name your price.

